These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, milk, iced-tea, almond-milk
Sport: rugby, golf, basketball, swimming
1. Beverage:mirinda is on the right of Sport:basketball##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far left##1
3. Sport:basketball is between Sport:golf and Beverage:milk##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:iced-tea is between Beverage:milk and Beverage:mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | milk   | iced-tea | mirinda       |
| Sport      | swimming | rugby | basketball   | golf |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: woodworking, singing, baking, board-games
Nationality: pakistani, mexican, american, japanese
1. Nationality:japanese is between Hobby:baking and Nationality:mexican##2
2. Hobby:board-games is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:american is on the right of Nationality:pakistani##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Nationality:pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | board-games |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese   | pakistani | american       |

